Type: Package
Package: PRcalc
Title: A Proportional Representation Calculator
Description: {PRcalc} is an R package designed for computing proportional representatives, computing disproportionality indices including alpha-divergence, and decomposing alpha-divergence. {PRcalc} can also be used to compute malapportionment in electoral district allocations.
Version: 0.8.7.2
